data.title: St. Louis Blues Emblem - Color
data.meta_description: NHL Exterior Auto Accessory - Color Emblem - 2" x 3.2"
data.text:
Bring your team on the road with you by featuring a Color Emblem from Sports Licensing Solutions! The 3D Emblem is constructed from metal and then plated with your team true colors, making sure these emblems are sure to really pop. The Enamel color plating helps the emblem resist the elements in any weather conditions, but to keep the colors bright just apply standard vehicle wax. With adhesive already applied to the back all you have to do is pick the spot you want the Emblem and place. The Emblem is also a great way to mark your laptop, golf cart, mailboxes, and much more. Roughly 3” x 3”, depending on team logo.

Made of heavy duty chrome and feature a molded 3D team logo with true team colors

Emblems resist the elements and look great for years

Easy to install, just peel and stick, it’s a breeze

Can be removed if wanted, and it will not damage your vehicle

Emblems can also be applied to laptops, mailboxes, golf carts, doors, and much more!

This item will ship in 2-business days

SLS Freight Grid

Shipping rates for individuals and resellers are as following:

If the order contains only Flashlights, Emblems, Headrest Covers, License Plate Frames, Decals, Air Fresheners or Bottle Openers, and if the total order amount is less than $20, then the following rates will be effective:

Due to higher shipping weight, a freight charge of $1.00/set or piece will be applied to vinyl car mats, vinyl door mats , vinyl cargo mats, deluxe mats, motorcycle mats, golf hitting mats, and tool boxes.

Shipments to P.O. Boxes, APO and FPO addresses can only be made via USPS. We cannot use FedEx or UPS for these shipments. If you have a FedEx or UPS shipper account and send us an order with a P.O. Box, APO, or FPO address we will use USPS for the shipment and bill you for the respective freight amount as per the above rates. APO and FPO address have an additional surcharge of $20 per order. P.O. Boxes have an additional surcharge of $10 per order. Shipments to Hawaii, Alaska, and Puerto Rico have an additional surcharge of $20 per order. SLS reserves the right to change product prices and freight charges at its sole discretion without notice.
